# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback for provider pages.
#
# Per-provider HTML files don't ship with the deployment — the static export
# emits one shell at /hospital/_unavailable/ and one at /nursing-home/_unavailable/.
# These rewrites route every per-provider URL to its respective shell, where a
# client component reads the URL, extracts the CCN, fetches from R2, and renders.
#
# Status 200 = internal rewrite (URL stays in browser, content served from shell).
# copy-redirects.js copies this file to out/ after next build because Next.js
# filters underscore-prefixed files from public/.

/hospital/*       /hospital/_unavailable/       200
/nursing-home/*   /nursing-home/_unavailable/   200
